nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROBLEM RUN# 510 FULL COV MODEL $INPUT C ID DV AMT II ADDL TIME RATE HT WT CLCR SEX AGE $DATA ../poppk_wcovs.csv IGNORE=C $SUB ADVAN1 TRANS2
$PK TVCL=THETA(1)*(CLCR/80)**THETA(3)*(AGE/45)**THETA(4) CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1)) TVV=THETA(2)*(WT/70)**THETA(5)*(AGE/45)**THETA(6) V=TVV*EXP(ETA(2)) S1=V $ERROR Y=F + F*ERR(1) IPRED=F
$THETA (0, 13) ;[L/day] CL (0, 75) ;[L] V (0.001 );[L/day] CL_{CLCR} (0.001) ;[L/day] CL_{AGE} (0.001) ;[L] V_{WT} (0.001) ;[L] V_{AGE}
$OMEGA BLOCK(2) ; a comment (0.04) ;[P] CL (0.02) ;[R] CL-V (0.04) ;[P] V
$SIGMA 0.04 ;[P] Residual
;$MSFI=./401.msf $EST METH=ITS INTERACTION PRINT=5 NITER=20 SIG=3 NOABORT MSFO=./510.msf $EST METH=1 INTERACTION PRINT=5 MAX=9999 SIG=3 NOABORT MSFO=./510.msf $EST METH=IMP INTERACTION PRINT=1 NITER=200 EONLY=0 NOABORT SIGL=9 CTYPE=3 MSFO=./510.msf $EST METH=IMP INTERACTION PRINT=1 NITER=10 ISAMPLE=2000 EONLY=1 NOABORT SIGL=9 MSFO=./510.msf $COV $TABLE NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE =./510 ID TIME IPRED EVID ETA1 ETA2 $TABLE NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=./510par.tab ID TIME ETA1 ETA2 HT WT CLCR SEX AGE EVID
